# Terms

- DS  data source

# A server table
To add all servers from DS to the servers table you need:
- Add DS to Grafana configuration (Configuration  Data sources  Add data source);
- Open the dashboard;
- Click the table header  Edit;
- In the Query tab select Data source  Mixed;
- Click + Query;
- Select the desired DS;
- Paste query:

```sql
SELECT "ip", "n_cpus", "ram_total", "drive_total", "load15", "cpu_usage_percent", "ram_used_percent", last("drive_used_percent") AS "drive_used_percent" FROM "for_table" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "host"

```

- Select Table in the Format as value;
- Click Apply to save the panel;
- Click the floppy disk icon button on the top right to save dashboard changes.
